i Thuận</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A3n-T%E1%BB%8Bnh-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/Nh%E1%BA%A5t-qu%E1%BB%B9/poem-hDp1QmQyvwR_eesYIclmqw">Nhất quỹ - 一揆</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A3n-T%E1%BB%8Bnh-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-RlRhBIujgoZM-FwwiI42TA">Bản Tịnh thiền sư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/Qu%C3%A1-Ho%C3%A0nh-S%C6%A1n/poem-6RvgsR8BSo53V_Xe8R68ww">Quá Hoành Sơn - 過橫山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/author-DYGad0thHvgCxK3Szp1zVQ">Trần Đình Túc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-%C4%91o%E1%BA%A3n-c%C3%BA-ng%C3%A2m/poem-0vGlfCzjqWHY9ygox9A2fw">Trường đoản cú ngâm - 長短句吟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/V%E1%BB%8Dng-Phu-s%C6%A1n/poem-sH1o_RLNRtrWbBHaL1M7NA">Vọng Phu sơn - 望夫山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
